        >
          <h4 class="text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.5rem]">HEDGEHOG</h4>
          <h6 class="text-[1.5rem] font-thin text-primary sm:text-[1.75rem]">Adventurer</h6>
          <div class="px-3">
